  "title": "Pet Retail Sales Assistant #81263",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Pet Supplies/ Retail</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Singapore Islandwide (Travelling required)</li><li>Working Hours: 6 Days per week (9.30am – 9.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Meal & Transport Allowance + Commission + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver professional, proactive customer service and provide suitable product recommendations.</li><li>Handle cashiering and payment transactions.</li><li>Receive incoming stock, replenish shelves, and ensure proper product display.</li><li>Monitor product expiry dates and shelf-life to maintain stock quality.</li><li>Pick and pack items according to customers’ orders.</li><li>Carry out daily housekeeping to maintain a clean and tidy outlet.</li><li>Advise customers on pet care related inquiries</li><li>Support other ad-hoc duties as assigned by management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Able to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays.</li><li>Able to handle loads up to 10kg (trolley assistance provided)</li><li>Willing to travel within Singapore branch when required.</li><li>Strong interpersonal skills; able to work independently and collaborate effectively within a team.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81263 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
